seedu.addressbook.data.person

Interface ReadOnlyPerson

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Person

    public interface ReadOnlyPerson
    A read-only immutable interface for a Person in the addressbook. Implementations should guarantee: details are present and not null, field values are validated.
